IMPORTANT POWERSHELL COMMANDS:



FILE AND DIRECTORY COMMANDS:
pwd                                                                show current path-location
ls                                                                 list folder contentz
cd                                                                 switch to folder
cd..                                                               switch one level upward
mkdir                                                              make directory/folder of followong path name
rmdir                                                              remove/delete folder of following path name
New-Item -Path "C:\_some_pathname" iItemType File                  make file of listed location and name
Remove-Item "<path-and-filename>" -Recurse                         remove file
